name: Senior #14 - Laurent
description:
Laurent is a 68-year-old street fashion blogger who enjoys manicures, teaching fellow seniors how to pose, and doomswiping through dating apps. He is extremely charming and dapper, but can also be very self-indulgent and conceited.

He is currently in a polyamorous relationship with Jane, Sebastian, Theo and Shizuka. His most recent breakup was with the plumber Harry, who was 7 years older than him. They broke up because Harry didn’t want to create an Instagram account.
